headline: What CoStar Group (CSGP)'s AI‑Powered Smart Search Means for Shareholders
summary: Earlier this week, Homes.com, a leading online residential marketplace under CoStar Group, announced the launch of Smart Search, introducing advanced AI and natural language capabilities to streamline the home search process. This move is notable for enabling consumers to search listings in conversational language, marking a significant shift toward more personalized and accessible property search experiences. headline: 3 Services Stocks Walking a Fine Line
summary: Business services providers thrive by solving complex operational challenges for their clients, allowing them to focus on their secret sauce. These firms have helped their customers unlock huge efficiencies, so it’s no surprise the industry has posted a 30.2% gain over the past six months, beating the S&P 500 by 4.7 percentage points.
